Background

		Mr. Edgar R. Smith, III has been the President of Smitty's Supply, Inc. since 2001 and has been its Chairman Since 2001. Mr. Smith has been a Director of First Guaranty Bancshares, Inc. since October 16, 2014 and for its a subsidiary First Guaranty Bank since 2007.	
	



